```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Bean & Brew</title>
<style>
body {
margin 0; padding 0;
background: background-color: #fff;
font: font-size: 1;
nav a {
padding: 10px;
margin: 10px;
color: color: #fff;
background: background-color: #fff;
section {
background: background-color: #fff;
button {
background: background-color: #fff;
form {
background: background-color: #fff;
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Menu</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>
<section>
<h1>Bean & Brew</h1>
<p>Your coffee shop</p>
<button id="order">Order Now</button>
<form action="/submit">
<label>Name: <input type="text" name="name"></label>
<label>Email: <input type="email" name="email"></label>
<button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
<script>
document.getElementById("order").addEventListener("click", function() => alert("Thank you for your order!");
document.querySelector("form").addEventListener("submit", function() => preventDefault() => alert("Thank us for your order!")
</script>
</body>
</html>
```
